{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"加密","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在密码学（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">cryptography <small>(en-US)</small></a>）领域，<strong>加密</strong>是指把明文（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Plaintext\">plaintext</a>）转换成密文（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Ciphertext\">ciphertext</a>）的过程。密文应该对非授权用户不可读。</p>\n<p>加密是一个密码学原语：它通过一种称作 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cipher\">cipher</a> 的编码技术，把纯文本信息转换为密文。现代密码的加密算法是通过特定的密码算法来工作的，称为<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Key\">密钥</a>。由于算法常常是公开的，若要保证加密安全，就必须确保密钥高度保密。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Encryption/encryption.png\" alt=\"How encryption works.\" width=\"472\" height=\"108\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>如果不知道密钥，其逆过程<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption\">解密</a>在数学上是很难做到的。究竟有多难做到，取决于算法的安全性，以及<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptanalysis\">密码分析学 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的发展程度。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"在密码学（cryptography (en-US)）领域，加密是指把明文（plaintext）转换成密文（ciphertext）的过程。密文应该对非授权用户不可读。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Encryption","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Encriptación","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Chiffrement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Encryption (暗号化)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/encryption","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/encryption/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Encryption","title":"加密"}],"pageTitle":"加密 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}